text: Francisc Cociş (born 19 May 1930) is a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Satu Mare County
